Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveEbuka Obi Uchendu’s wife  Cynthia on Thursday listed 40 reasons why she adores her husband.

The Big Brother Naija host turned 40 on Thursday.

She posted a video on her Instagram page with the remark, “This is 40. 40 reasons why I love you,” in honor of his birthday.
